SN  - 0020-6598
UR  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1468-2354.2005.00324.x
Y2  - 2024/03/26
N2  - Three classes of models on money closely related to game theoretic models are (i) search theoretic models; (ii) repeated games (in a narrow sense); and (iii) trading post games. This note tries to point out the sense of affinity between the theory of microfoundations of money and the theory of ?repeated games? in a broad sense of the term.
ER  - 

