AU  - Berentsen, Aleksander
AU  - Camera, Gabriele
AU  - Waller, Christopher
Y1  - 2005/05/01
PY  - 2005
DA  - 2005/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1468-2354.2005.00329.x
T2  - International Economic Review
